chunk_content: Provide context on: • The status of birth cohort monitoring in your operating unit, geographic area or partner/implementing mechanism, including any planned activities. • The data source used for reporting, and any key information about data quality that is important for interpretation of results (see MER reference sheet for examples). • The number and proportion of PEPFAR-supported PMTCT sites implementing cohort monitoring and able to (1) report on PMTCT_FO and (2) longitudinally track mothers to assess continuity of treatment/viral suppression. 3. Provide context on trends for the proportion of infants with an unknown outcome (the sum of “unknown” plus “died” over time.
